item.description:
@Mitko wrote:

So you want to know if it’s online or not? Simply try to access your server with your no-ip instead of localhost or 127.0.0.1 and such. If it works then it should be online cause when i had such problems, the only way of logging in was by localhost so that means it wasn’t working but when i fixed my problem, logging through no-ip started to work.
